title: Dorshi khwmsi jabwgou, be buhumni bicayao
lyrics:
Dorshi khwmsi jabwgou, be buhumni bicayao
Barhunka bw barbwgou, bwi nuhornai krusnifai -2
(A)
Sanso haywi dukhu swina 
Bangarbai nwng papni biban -2
Thanki dongwmwn gwthar bijabao
Sakhi domgwmwn gwthar bijab -2
(B)
Papni mulug khou basainai khai
Swiya Porbu nwng khou be songsara -2
Mithiya Porbu nwngkhou dinwi
Baogar langbai be muluga -2
